description:
Beth Behrs [2 Broke Girls, The Neighborhood] joins Anna to talk about their days together on the Warner Brothers lot, mental health, music, therapy horses, her new podcast Harmonics with Beth Behrs, how Sweet Valley High qualifies as erotic literature and more. Later in the episode Anna welcomes back Professor Eli Finkel who has some qualified insight to offer us all.
